headline: Netflix: A Proven Winner, but a Stock Priced for Perfection
summary: Netflix has a proven model and growth potential, but high valuation and weak institutional conviction make the stock less compelling.

headline: Disney Vs. Netflix: Christmas Streaming Wars And What It Means For The Stocks
summary: Families settling in for Christmas movie marathons this week are giving Wall Street another reason to watch Walt Disney Co (NYSE:DIS) and Netflix Inc (NASDAQ:NFLX). Here’s what investors need to know. What To Know: Walt Disney shares traded around $114 on Christmas Eve, up 3% year-to-date, as investors leaned into a holiday slate led by classics on Disney+ and Hulu.
